name: PhiHenna Burgundy
short_description: Phi Henna is an eyebrow dye made from henna, indented for eyebrow coloring, resulting with definition and rich color of naturally sculpted brows.
long_description: Beside the effect similar to permanent makeup Phi Henna, with all its natural benefits, provides multiple advantages for the brow hairs by helping to refine and revive weak eyebrow hair follicles, encouraging their vitality and keeping their natural shape. Phi Henna color easily tints the skin leaving subtle effect of soft color, similar to a permanent makeup effect, with no unwanted reddish or blue tones.Kit Contents:3 packets of PhiHennaMeasuring cupInstruction leafletSpatulaBottle to keep leftover PhiHenna
